flowchart TD
    START([Teacher selects student to screen]) --> A

    A[POST /session/start] --> B{Student valid\n& belongs to teacher?}
    B -- No --> ERR1([Error: Student not found / Access denied])
    B -- Yes --> C[HRAT Engine creates in-memory session\nSession ID generated]

    C --> D[/Phase 1: Gateway Questions\nQ1–Q5 — one per LD domain/]

    D --> E[Teacher answers Q on 1–5 scale]
    E --> F[HRAT records answer\nUpdates domain suspicion score]
    F --> G{All 5 gateway\nquestions done?}
    G -- No --> E
    G -- Yes --> H

    H[/Phase 2: Domain-Prioritised Questions\nRank domains by suspicion score/]
    H --> H1["Rank 1 & 2 → 4 deep-dive Qs each\nRank 3 → 2 Qs\nRank 4 & 5 → 1 Q each\n= 12 questions"]
    H1 --> I[Teacher answers domain-specific Q]
    I --> J[HRAT routes next question by priority]
    J --> K{12 questions\ncomplete?}
    K -- No --> I
    K -- Yes --> L

    L[/Phase 3: Fill Questions\nQ18–Q20 from highest-suspicion gaps/]
    L --> M[Teacher answers 3 fill questions]
    M --> N{All 20 questions\ncomplete?}
    N -- No --> M
    N -- Yes --> O

    O[Teacher submits observation notes\nOptional free-text] --> P

    P[POST /session/complete] --> Q[HRAT finalize\nBuild feature vector — 20 averaged scores]

    Q --> R{Observation notes\nprovided?}
    R -- Yes --> S[NLP Analyzer — spaCy\nLemmatize + keyword match\nDetect LD indicators in text]
    S --> T
    R -- No --> T

    T[ML Model — MultiOutputClassifier\npredict_with_explanation] --> U[SHAP TreeExplainer\nCompute feature contributions per LD\nRank top 3 features]

    U --> V[Generate human-readable narrative\nper LD with probability + key indicators]

    V --> W[Save Screening record to DB\nanswers + nlp_notes]
    W --> X[Save PredictionResult to DB\n5 LD probability scores]
    X --> Y[Delete in-memory session]

    Y --> Z([Display results to Teacher\nLD scores + SHAP explanation + NLP flags])
